/a> 接口。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"标准","id":"标准"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"PerformanceTiming.connectStart 是一个返回代表一个时刻的 unsigned long long 型只读属性，请求连接被发送到网络之时的 Unix 毫秒时间戳。如果传输层报告错误并且连接的建立重新开始，则把最后建立连接的开始时间作为该值。如果一个持久连接被使用，则该值与 PerformanceTiming.fetchStart 相同。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PerformanceTiming.connectStart","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"PerformanceTiming.connectStart","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/performancetiming/connectstart","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/performancetiming/connectstart/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming","title":"PerformanceTiming"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/connectStart","title":"PerformanceTiming.connectStart"}],"pageTitle":"PerformanceTiming.connectStart - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}